data.description: This home is located in a beautiful area of Deep Creek section 20 and just 10-15 minutes to the interstate to take you to Ft. Myers or Port Charlotte for some amazing fishing. Close to shopping, restaurants and schools. This home has new barn window shutters, screen room, Hurricane shutters, home security and much more. For more information about this area, you can contact " Section 20 Property Owners Association" Deep Creek Community. www.deepcreekfl.com. Inspections are welcomed.
